Program: Great Lives
Title: Sir Alec Issigonis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b007x2pt
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 16 Sep 2016
Series of biographical discussions with Matthew Parris. 4/9. Engineer Alex Moulton and the Earl of Snowdon talk about the life of Alec Issigonis, the idiosyncratic designer of the Mini.